      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIZOOLOGIST (3) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Cornhill Raven (26.83) in a T3 RSTW. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Rates highly and will give a great sight. REGAL ALLY (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (34.79) at Sandown behind Boracay Bella in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can feature again. OKAY ALF (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (27.09) last time in a T3 RSTW at this track. Shapes as one to consider. PAW UNITY (7) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
